<ns2816:section xmlns:ns2816="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.platforms.linux.networkServices.dns.exercise">

	<ns2817:title xmlns:ns2817="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Domain Name Server (DNS) Exercise</ns2817:title>
	<ns2818:para xmlns:ns2818="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
	Pair up with a partner and configure a primary, as well as a secondary DNS server on each of your workstations. Then add your two workstations to the zone on the primary server, and perform a zone transfer to the secondary server.
	</ns2818:para>
